#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-kbruch.1.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid "Learn calculating with fractions and percentages"
msgstr "Aprender a calcular con fraccións e porcentaxes."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-kbruch.1.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
