#. Tag: title
#: man-kbruch.1.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Descrición"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbruch.1.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kbruch; is a small program to practice calculating with fractions and "
"percentages. Different exercises are provided for this purpose. The program "
"checks user's input and gives feedback."
msgstr ""
"&kbruch; é un pequeno programa para practicar o cálculo con fraccións e "
"porcentaxes. Fornece distintos exercicios con esta fin. O programa comproba "
"o que escribes e responde en consecuencia."

